
Welcome to Beryllium OS.

The programs included with the beryllium os system are free software.
A manual is included within the default directory, and the exact LICENCE
is provided within the source repo: https://github.com/beryllium-org/OS

Beryllium OS comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY, to the extent
permitted by applicable law.

For information on how to use beryllium os, run "man beryllium".
To exit GNU/Screen, press Ctrl + A then K and y.
To exit Tio, press Ctrl + T then q.

